title: Week 12 - The Return Of Rico Bosco
description:
Big Cat, Lightswitch and Hank are joined in studio this week by the one, the only, Rico Bosco to break down all of the week 12 NCAAF games as well an intern tout contest update, the introduction of "The Lock Chain" & some delightful singing to end the show!


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/barstoolpickem
